Rogues get the same free, large upgrade in damage by dinging 63, and then 65.  Arilou, one of the better equipped warriors in my guild (Blade of Carnage, Braid of Golden Hair) parses 110ish dps against crypt of decay mobs.  That's around the highest our rogue pet can -ever- get under ideal circumstances (with the butt 100% of the time he was doing 85 melee, and I assume around 20 through procs and spells). Rogue we picked up from another high end guild (Using what looked like Khalshazar and Massive Heartwood Thorn) was doing 200ish in just melee.<br>
